The paper discusses the deployment aspects of 5G NR systems, which are related to networking and information theory (cs.NI, cs.IT). The focus is on the C-band and millimeter-wave bands, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and architecture (cs.AR) subcategories. The paper also presents a model derived from measured beam identities, which is related to mathematics (cs.MA).
